headline: Why DexCom (DXCM) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of medical device company DexCom (NASDAQ:DXCM) jumped 3.3% in the afternoon session after company executives provided an optimistic outlook at the Wells Fargo Healthcare Conference on Wednesday.

headline: Dexcom to lay off about 350 people
summary: The diabetes technology company said the cuts are part of broader changes to its structure, including eliminating operations roles in San Diego and shifting those positions to Arizona.
